description:
This template is designed to faciliate the development of standard operating procedures (SOPs) in an academic research setting.&nbsp; 
 The template includes an example SOP for a vital scientific process - making coffee.&nbsp; 
 Please take the elements of this that work best for you and discard what doesn't. The purpose is not to perscribe one particular way of brewing coffee (or formatting an SOP), just to catelyze the development of SOPs to standardize and guide research-related activities.

